  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK383">
<l>tūṅkāmai kalvi tuṇivuṭaimai yimmūṉṟu</l>
<l>nīṅkā nilaṉāḷ pavaṟku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These three things, viz., vigilance, learning, and bravery, should never be wanting in the ruler of a country.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
